snippet.title: Best VGM 2218 - Pac Man World 3 - Spectral Zenith ~ Puzzle
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameCube / PS2 / Xbox / NDS / PSP / PC
Pac Man World 3 (2004)
Spectral Zenith ~ Puzzle
Matt Black, Rob Blake, John Guscott & Chris Hockey

Twitter: https://twitter.com/SupraDarky
